 |archivedate = 2009-02-08
}}</ref>

IETF在互联网草案中描述了LEDBAT算法，<ref>{{cite web
 | url = http://tools.ietf.org/id/draft-shalunov-ledbat-congestion-00.txt
 | date = 2009-03-04
